statements: SELECT * FROM water_conservation_campaign;
SELECT program_name, outreach_date FROM water_conservation_campaign;
SELECT num_participants, water_saved FROM water_conservation_campaign WHERE num_participants > 50;
SELECT * FROM water_conservation_campaign ORDER BY outreach_date DESC;
SELECT program_name, water_saved FROM water_conservation_campaign WHERE water_saved >= 1000;
SELECT * FROM water_conservation_campaign WHERE num_participants > 100 ORDER BY outreach_date DESC;
SELECT program_name, water_saved FROM water_conservation_campaign WHERE water_saved > 5000;
SELECT campaign_id, program_name, outreach_date, num_participants, water_saved FROM water_conservation_campaign ORDER BY num_participants DESC;
SELECT AVG(water_saved) AS avg_water_saved FROM water_conservation_campaign;
SELECT program_name, outreach_date, num_participants FROM water_conservation_campaign WHERE outreach_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM outreach_programs
SELECT program_name, start_date FROM outreach_programs
SELECT program_id, program_name, end_date FROM outreach_programs
SELECT * FROM program_participants
SELECT participant_id, program_id, city FROM program_participants
SELECT * FROM outreach_programs
SELECT program_name, start_date, end_date FROM outreach_programs ORDER BY start_date DESC
SELECT participant_name, city FROM program_participants WHERE registration_date > '2022-01-01'
SELECT program_name, participant_name FROM outreach_programs INNER JOIN program_participants ON outreach_programs.program_id = program_participants.program_id
SELECT * FROM outreach_programs WHERE start_date < '2022-06-01' ORDER BY program_name
SELECT * FROM outreach_programs;
SELECT program_name, program_type FROM outreach_programs WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT program_name, end_date FROM outreach_programs WHERE program_type = 'Educational';
SELECT participant_id, participant_name, contact_email FROM program_participants ORDER BY registration_date DESC;
SELECT feedback_text, feedback_date FROM program_feedback WHERE program_id = 3 AND participant_id = 5;
SELECT * FROM outreach_programs ORDER BY program_id DESC;
SELECT program_id, program_name, program_type FROM outreach_programs WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01' AND end_date < '2022-12-31';
SELECT program_id, COUNT(participant_id) AS participants_count FROM program_participants GROUP BY program_id HAVING participants_count > 5;
SELECT feedback_id, feedback_text FROM program_feedback WHERE feedback_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2022-12-31 23:59:59';

SELECT DISTINCT p.program_id, p.program_name, pp.participant_name FROM outreach_programs p INNER JOIN program_participants pp ON p.program_id = pp.program_id ORDER BY p.program_id ASC, pp.participant_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM campaign;
SELECT campaign_name, start_date, end_date FROM campaign WHERE campaign_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM outreach_program ORDER BY program_name DESC;
SELECT program_name, program_type FROM outreach_program WHERE targeting_audience = 'Youth';
SELECT result_id, outcome, effectiveness_rating FROM outreach_results WHERE effectiveness_rating > 3 ORDER BY result_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM campaign WHERE campaign_id = 1;
SELECT campaign_name, start_date, end_date FROM campaign WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01' AND end_date < '2023-01-01';
SELECT program_name, outreach_location FROM outreach_program JOIN outreach_tracking ON outreach_program.program_id = outreach_tracking.program_id;

SELECT outreach_results.outcome, outreach_results.effectiveness_rating, outreach_tracking.outreach_date FROM outreach_results LEFT JOIN outreach_tracking ON outreach_results.tracking_id = outreach_tracking.tracking_id;

SELECT campaign.campaign_name, outreach_program.program_name, outreach_tracking.outreach_location, outreach_results.outcome FROM campaign JOIN outreach_program ON campaign.campaign_id = outreach_program.program_id JOIN outreach_tracking ON outreach_program.program_id = outreach_tracking.program_id JOIN outreach_results ON outreach_tracking.tracking_id = outreach_results.tracking_id;
SELECT * FROM OutreachPrograms;
SELECT program_name, outreach_type FROM OutreachPrograms ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM Participants WHERE participant_id = 1;
SELECT program_name, start_date, end_date FROM OutreachPrograms WHERE outreach_type = 'Environment';
SELECT participant_name, email, address FROM Participants WHERE contact_number LIKE '%123%';
SELECT * FROM OutreachPrograms;
SELECT program_name, start_date, end_date FROM OutreachPrograms ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT program_name, outreach_type, COUNT(program_id) AS num_programs FROM OutreachPrograms GROUP BY outreach_type HAVING COUNT(program_id) > 1;

SELECT Participants.participant_name, ProgramFeedback.rating, ProgramFeedback.feedback_text FROM Participants JOIN ProgramFeedback ON Participants.participant_id = ProgramFeedback.participant_id WHERE ProgramFeedback.rating >= 4;

SELECT program_name, sessions.session_date, sessions.location FROM OutreachPrograms JOIN Sessions ON OutreachPrograms.program_id = Sessions.program_id WHERE sessions.session_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY sessions.session_date ASC;
